## 🧠 What This System Does

Most CRMs are databases with a UI on top. This is different — it's a **memory-driven AI operating system** for sales where every lead interaction, status change, and decision is stored, tracked, and surfaced intelligently.

The AI layer operates **strictly on structured stored data** — not probabilistic model outputs — which eliminates hallucination entirely and makes every response reliable and auditable.

